1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:10,000

5
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:07,100
宇宙中心的矗立着一座塔 保护宇宙防止黑暗力量侵袭

6
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:13,300
据说某位儿童的灵知之力能摧毁这座塔

7
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:22,600
黑 暗 塔

8
00:01:37,990 --> 00:01:39,780
来和我们一起玩吧 快来呀
Come and play with us. Come and play.

9
00:01:42,580 --> 00:01:45,120
- 你抓不到我  - 想得美
- Not gonna get me!  - You wish!

10
00:03:31,900 --> 00:03:34,690
- 杰克  - 妈妈 你还好吗？
- Jake.  - Mom, you okay?

11
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:38,360
刚刚那次地震可真不小
That was a big one.

12
00:03:40,900 --> 00:03:42,200
又做噩梦了？
Bad dreams?

13
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:44,410
没有
No.

14
00:03:46,410 --> 00:03:48,160
来吧 去吃早饭
Come on. Get breakfast.

15
00:04:00,340 --> 00:04:03,470
今早的地震给上班族带来了不小的麻烦
This morning's quake is causing major problems for commuters.

16
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:07,680
纽约今早遭遇五点七级地震
The 5.7-magnitude quake hit New York early this morning.

17
00:04:07,850 --> 00:04:11,190
然而太平洋两岸也受到一系列地震袭扰
Yet another in a series of quakes that has rattled both coasts.

18
00:04:11,350 --> 00:04:15,060
东京再次发生地震 再加上上周的柏林地震…
Tokyo was hit again. And with the Berlin quake last week...

19
00:04:15,230 --> 00:04:18,280
问题就来了 是什么引起了这些地震？
Question is: What is causing all these earthquakes?

20
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:21,740
天哪 现在连体育娱乐频道也在报道地震了
Christ, even ESPN's doing the quakes now.

21
00:04:21,900 --> 00:04:24,570
但目前地震原因尚不清楚
But we still don't know what's causing them.

22
00:04:24,740 --> 00:04:26,280
嗨 我爸妈让我过来看看…
Hey. My folks sent me over to see...

23
00:04:26,450 --> 00:04:28,330
- …你们是不是还活着  - 我们很好 蒂米
- ...if you guys are still alive.  - We're fine, Timmy.

24
00:04:28,490 --> 00:04:29,950
那地震可真够强的
That was pretty intense.

25
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,500
- 是啊  - 你还好吧？
- Yeah.  - You good?

26
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:34,880
- 还好  - 我们迟会到
- Yeah.  - We're just running a little late.

27
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:37,170
- 一会见？ - 替我跟你妈妈问个好
- See you later?  - Say hi to your mom for me.

28
00:04:37,340 --> 00:04:39,210
妈妈 劳里跟你问好
Ma, Laurie says hi.

29
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:41,470
别忘了 你下课后要去见霍奇基斯博士
Don't forget, you have Dr. Hotchkiss after school.

30
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:51,520
我们找这些心理医生根本就是浪费钱
We're wasting money on all those shrinks.

31
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,690
他已经好些了
He's making progress.

32
00:05:19,710 --> 00:05:21,260
等一下
Wait up!

33
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:27,260
嘿 你从我的存物柜里拿了那些书吗？
Hey, did you get the books from my locker?

34
00:05:28,220 --> 00:05:29,720
所以你说世界末日什么时候到来呢？
So when's the apocalypse coming?

35
00:05:29,890 --> 00:05:32,100
拜托了 你就把书还给我吧
Come on, man, just give me my book.

36
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:35,390
- 怎么 你吃的药不管用了？ - 嘿 嘿
- What's wrong, your meds stop working?  - Hey! Hey!

37
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,310
- 把书还给我  - 你先下去
- Give me my book!  - Get off me!

38
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,190
- 下去  - 嘿
- Get off of me.  - Hey!

39
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,440
嘿 够了 钱伯斯
Hey. That is enough, Chambers.

40
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,360
把书还给我
I need my book.

41
00:05:45,490 --> 00:05:49,030
嘿 你得回家冷静冷静
Hey. You need to go home and cool off.

42
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:56,250
你最近 一直挺忙的啊 杰克
You've been, uh, quite busy, Jake.

43
00:06:00,460 --> 00:06:03,670
你觉得最近的这些地震…
This big tower in the clouds you keep dreaming about...

44
00:06:05,340 --> 00:06:09,180
…与经常在你梦里出现的那个云雾缭绕的高塔有关
...you say these earthquakes we've been having have something to do with it.

45
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:13,520
发生地震是因为那座塔在遭受袭击
They happen because the Tower is under attack.

46
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:20,480
你是个聪明孩子 杰克
You're a smart kid, Jake.

47
00:06:20,650 --> 00:06:22,150
你要明白当你无法…
You know when you can't differentiate...

48
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:24,820
- …区分梦境与现实的时候…  - 那不是梦
- ...between dreams and reality...  - It's not a dream.

49
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:26,110
好吗？我不是疯子
Okay? I'm not crazy.

50
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:28,740
我一直看到同样的事物
I always see the same thing.

51
00:06:28,910 --> 00:06:32,660
黑暗塔 黑衣人 还有穿着蒙面的怪人
The Tower, the Man in Black, the creepy guys with the fake skins.

52
00:06:35,620 --> 00:06:38,420
如果那座塔被摧毁了会怎样？
What if the Tower were destroyed?

53
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:42,290
世界会陷入无尽的黑暗和烈火之中
Darkness and fire.

54
00:06:45,590 --> 00:06:47,380
我们来谈谈你的父亲
Let's talk about your dad.

55
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:51,680
又谈这个
Surprise.

56
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:55,100
你失去了父亲 你的世界崩塌了
When you lost your father, your world fell apart.

57
00:06:56,020 --> 00:06:58,390
你之所以出现末日迫近的幻觉…
You have these visions of impending hell on Earth...

58
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:01,730
…正是因为这恰恰是你内心的感受
...because that's how you feel inside.

59
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:04,480
即便是“黑暗”和“烈火”这些字眼…
Even words like "darkness" and "fire"...

60
00:07:04,650 --> 00:07:08,360
…杰克啊 你也是在描述你父亲牺牲的那晚
...Jake, you're describing the night your father died.

61
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:10,910
肯定没这么简单
Can't just be about that.

62
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,570
杰克 那只是梦而已
They're just dreams, Jake.

63
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:15,490
不是真的
They're not real.

64
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,440
一定要小心
Watch out.

65
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:46,360
他们会把你抓走
They'll take you.

66
00:07:46,530 --> 00:07:47,730
他们专抓像你这样的孩子
They steal kids like you.

67
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,240
快到路对面去
Cross them over.

68
00:07:51,490 --> 00:07:52,530
你们与众不同
Special ones.

69
00:07:53,740 --> 00:07:56,990
他们想控制你们的头脑
The power of your mind, that's what they want.

70
00:08:14,010 --> 00:08:16,680
杰克 你没事吧？
Jake. What's up?

71
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:18,770
今天诸事不顺么？
Bad day?

72
00:08:18,930 --> 00:08:20,390
是
Yeah.

73
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:22,140
走吧
Let's go.

74
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:23,730
- 想一块出去玩吗？ - 好啊
- Want to hang out?  - Yeah.

75
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:26,270
…控制 他状况很不稳定 我们就接受提议吧
...control, he's unstable. We need to take the offer.

76
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:29,280
- 这是免费接受高水平治疗的好机会  - 这不是钱的问题
- It's great treatment for no money.  - It's not about the money.

77
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,690
- 我在你房间里等着  - 我们现在…
- I'll wait in your room.  - There's nothing more...

78
00:08:30,860 --> 00:08:32,110
- …已经帮不了他了  - 天哪 朗
- ...we can do for him now.  - Jesus, Lon!

79
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:35,240
你至少得装出一副把他当作亲生儿子的样子吧？
Can you at least pretend like he's your own kid?

80
00:08:38,370 --> 00:08:42,000
抱歉 宝贝 我们… 我们没听到你进来
I'm sorry, baby, we...  We didn't hear you come in.

81
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:44,120
今天在学校 到底是怎么回事？
What the hell happened in school today?

82
00:08:44,290 --> 00:08:46,710
你答应过我 不去惹事的
You promised me you're gonna stay out of trouble.

83
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:48,630
对不起 妈妈
Sorry, Mom.

84
00:08:50,210 --> 00:08:51,920
亲爱的 嗯…
Honey, um...

85
00:08:52,090 --> 00:08:55,550
…州北有一个诊所联系了你们学校
...the school's been approached by a clinic upstate.

86
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,550
他们专门帮助…
They work with kids who...

87
00:08:57,720 --> 00:09:00,350
正处在困难时期的孩子
Who are having a hard time.

88
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:02,230
这个周末有一个开放参观机会
There's an opening this weekend.

89
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:04,770
应该是个不错的地方
It's supposed to be a great place.

90
00:09:04,940 --> 00:09:07,310
做的研究都很科学 能做脑部扫描 还有睡眠模式研究
It's science-based: brain scans, sleep patterns.

91
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:10,280
- 我觉得能…  - 行 好吧
- I think it could...  - Yeah, okay.

92
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:16,410
伙计 那可就是疯人院啊
Man, psycho camp.

93
00:09:16,570 --> 00:09:17,740
肯定糟透了 哥们
Sucks, dude.

94
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:21,240
更多的心理医生 只会浪费更多时间
More shrinks. Waste of time.

95
00:09:29,590 --> 00:09:30,630
哥们
Dude.

96
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,130
怎么了？
What?

97
00:09:33,300 --> 00:09:34,760
别再盯着你那些画了
Stop staring at your drawings.

98
00:09:34,930 --> 00:09:36,300
你真是把我吓坏了
You're freaking me out.

99
00:09:38,010 --> 00:09:40,060
你也以为我疯了 是吧？
You think I'm crazy too, don't you?

100
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:41,890
胡说
Batshit.

101
00:09:48,770 --> 00:09:50,020
…我们之间越来越生疏
...driving us apart.

102
00:09:53,110 --> 00:09:55,110
我只是在请求…
I'm just asking...

103
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:57,280
我们需要帮助 我们俩都需要
We need help. We both need help.

104
00:09:57,450 --> 00:09:58,820
我们撑不下去了
We are falling apart.

105
00:09:58,990 --> 00:10:00,490
我非常爱他…
I love him so much...

106
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:04,330
…我不能再看着他这么下去了
...and I just can't stand to see him like this.

107
00:10:04,500 --> 00:10:07,170
他曾经多么无忧无虑
He was such a happy kid.

108
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:27,980
不要再做梦了
No more dreams.

109
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:30,480
就只静静地睡一晚
Just one night of sleep.

110
00:10:49,710 --> 00:10:53,340
我的朋友 你不用害怕
You have nothing to be afraid of, my friend.

111
00:10:54,380 --> 00:10:56,970
死亡并不遥远
Death is not far away.

112
00:10:57,670 --> 00:11:00,640
想知道世界另一边都有什么吗？
You want to know what's on the other side?

113
00:11:01,220 --> 00:11:03,350
你能看到吗？
Can you see it?

114
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:07,310
当然不能
Of course you can't.

115
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:09,640
因为那里什么都没有
Because nothing is there.

116
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:13,440
- 天堂地狱的那一套都是谎言  - 你下地狱吧
- It's all a lie.  - Go to hell.

117
00:11:13,690 --> 00:11:16,230
我早去过地狱了 现在燃烧吧
Been there. Now burn.

118
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:29,710
我们失败了
We lost.

119
00:11:30,540 --> 00:11:32,250
不 枪侠不倒
Not while the Tower still stands.

120
00:11:32,420 --> 00:11:33,960
塔就不倒
Not while you still stand.

121
00:11:40,300 --> 00:11:42,090
别让他进入你的头脑中
Don't let him get into your head.

122
00:11:42,260 --> 00:11:44,050
两位枪侠
Gunslingers.

123
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:48,770
枪准不在于双手
I do not aim with my hand.

124
00:11:48,930 --> 00:11:51,900
- 违此者…  - 忘祖也
- He who aims with his hand...  - Has forgotten the face of his father.

125
00:11:52,060 --> 00:11:53,270
枪准在于双眼
I aim with my eye.

126
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:55,440
枪侠 我在这儿呢
Gunslinger, over here.

127
00:11:56,690 --> 00:11:58,740
枪准不在于双手
I do not shoot with my hand.

128
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:01,820
违此者 忘祖也
He who shoots with his hand has forgotten the face of his father.

129
00:12:01,990 --> 00:12:03,700
- 枪准在于头脑  - 枪侠
- I shoot with my mind.  - Gunslingers.

130
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,450
枪准不在于所用之枪
I do not kill with my gun.

131
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:11,670
违此者 忘祖也
He who kills with his gun has forgotten the face of his father.

132
00:12:12,790 --> 00:12:13,960
枪准在于我的心
I kill with my heart.

133
00:12:15,210 --> 00:12:16,290
停止呼吸
Stop breathing.

134
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,590
不
No.

135
00:12:23,890 --> 00:12:25,350
吸气
Breathe.

136
00:12:25,510 --> 00:12:27,390
用力反抗 不要放弃
Fight it. Fight it!

137
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:39,280
这招对你从不管用 是吧 罗兰？
It never works on you, does it, Roland?

138
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:43,410
你这种抗拒我法力的能力…
The power you have to resist my magics...

139
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:47,030
只是暂时的
Not forever.

140
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:50,660
你转过身来
Face me!

141
00:12:51,540 --> 00:12:53,160
看着我
Face me.

142
00:12:58,710 --> 00:13:01,300
罗兰 黑暗塔终将倒塌的
The Tower will fall, Roland.

143
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:05,470
后会有期了 老伙计
Until next time, old friend.

144
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:12,230
黑衣人匆忙奔过沙漠…
The Man in Black fled across the desert...

145
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:13,890
…枪侠紧随其后
...and the Gunslinger followed.

146
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,610
该死
Holy shit.

147
00:13:23,070 --> 00:13:25,280
- 嗨  - 这个人 他是某种战士
- Hey.  - This guy, he's some kind of soldier.

148
00:13:26,410 --> 00:13:27,950
被称作枪侠
He's called a Gunslinger.

149
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:30,200
你再看这个房子 外面挂着一个联邦邮箱
And this house, look, it's got a U.S. mailbox.

150
00:13:30,370 --> 00:13:32,580
- 我觉得这房子就在纽约  - 蒂米 七点了
- I think it's in New York.  - Timmy, it's 7 a.m.

151
00:13:32,750 --> 00:13:34,080
该跟你朋友说再见了
Time to say goodbye.

152
00:13:34,250 --> 00:13:37,000
抱歉 我得走了 稍后跟你联系
Sorry, got to go. Talk to you later.

153
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:56,770
那家诊所的人来了
The people from the clinic are here.

154
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:58,980
就现在？
Now?

155
00:13:59,150 --> 00:14:00,860
我不能… 我现在不能走
I can't... I can't go now.

156
00:14:01,020 --> 00:14:02,530
你必须走 杰克
You got to step up, Jake.

157
00:14:02,690 --> 00:14:05,320
即便不是为了你自己 也要为你母亲着想
If you won't do it for yourself, then do it for your mom.

158
00:14:06,990 --> 00:14:09,490
- 其他小孩也是这样吗？ - 这种情况很常见
- It's in other boys?  - It's common in adolescent boys.

159
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,620
他来了
There he is.

160
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:13,790
杰克 你好
Hi there, Jake.

161
00:14:13,950 --> 00:14:15,250
我是吉尔
I'm Jill.

162
00:14:15,410 --> 00:14:18,250
我是你的主治医师
I'm your intake administration supervisor.

163
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,420
这是我们的司机 托比
This is Toby, our driver.

164
00:14:20,590 --> 00:14:22,300
你好啊 小伙子
How's it going, young man?

165
00:14:22,460 --> 00:14:23,760
你打包好行李了吗？
You pack your things?

166
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:25,800
你们诊所具体是做什么的？
What exactly do they do at your clinic?

167
00:14:25,970 --> 00:14:29,140
杰克 他们和校方已经合作很久了
Jake, these guys have been working with the school for a long time.

168
00:14:29,300 --> 00:14:31,470
没关系 劳里 我们鼓励孩子提问的
No, that's okay, Laurie. We encourage questions.

169
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:34,060
这展现出他很精神 很有活力
It shows spirit and vitality.

170
00:14:34,220 --> 00:14:36,180
看起来是一个很健康的小孩子
He's just a healthy growing boy.

171
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:38,900
我可以和你保证我们所有的测试都是在
I can assure you that all our tests are done in a controlled...

172
00:14:39,060 --> 00:14:41,400
…很友好的环境下进行的
...child-friendly environment.

173
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:43,650
我们处理过很多类似的情况
We have experience with cases like yours.

174
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:46,950
比如睡觉惊醒 出现幻觉 痴迷的症状
Night terrors, hallucinations, odd obsessions.

175
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:50,280
相比标准治疗 我们的治疗其实很温柔
Our approach is actually very gentle compared to standard treatments.

176
00:14:50,450 --> 00:14:53,330
我知道你在担心 其实你一点也不用害怕
I understand your concerns, but you don't have to worry at all.

177
00:14:55,370 --> 00:14:57,040
妈妈 帮我打包一下东西 好么？
Mom, help me pack?

178
